description: Ten Farnsworth is an award-winning, boutique building located in Boston’s vibrant Seaport district. Luxurious finishes and a serene palette define this 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home with direct elevator access, a superb layout, all on a single floor. The finest materials and craftsmanship have gone into every detail of the dramatic, open floor plan, surrounded by floor-to-ceiling windows. The chef’s kitchens boast marble countertops, custom European cabinetry, and Gaggenau appliances. The kitchen flows effortlessly to the dining and living room beyond. The living room is anchored with a gas fireplace, and all rooms feature wide plank European oak flooring. The large primary suite is finished with Italian built-in wardrobes, and a stunning marble bath. 1 garage parking in the building, smart home technology, and a common outdoor roof deck, complete this elegant home. This home is legally a 3 bedroom.
